Package: HEART
Type: Package
Title: HEART: A high-efficiency and robust test for large scale single-cell RNA-sequencing differential expression analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xin Yuan <yuanxin_yx@sjtu.edu.cn>
Maintainer: Xin Yuan <yuanxin_yx@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: HEART, a statistical combination test, 
	can easily capture the various source of the difference beyond mean expression changes 
	and facilitate the accuracy, robustness, and efficiency of single-cell DE analysis. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), matrixTests
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
